# ===== Secrets / local config =====
# The Spoonacular key is read from the SPOONACULAR_API_KEY environment variable.
# Never commit a real key. These files are ignored so local secrets can't leak:
.env
.env.*
secrets.properties
config.properties
application-local.properties
application-secret.properties
application-secrets.properties

